  "prompt": "Why did Quora acquire Parlio?",
  "response": "Quora acquired Parlio to enhance its platform by integrating Parlio's features and expertise in fostering meaningful discussions and debates. Parlio was known for its focus on high-quality conversations and attracting experts and thought leaders in various fields. By acquiring Parlio, Quora aimed to improve its question-and-answer format, encourage more in-depth and engaging discussions, and expand its user base with Parlio's community. This move was part of Quora's strategy to evolve and offer a more comprehensive and interactive experience for its users.",
